column5: I was out with a very good buddy who I don't get the opportunity to fish with to much anymore. We killed 5 hours together yesterday on a lake searching for a 5# plus brookie to take a few pics with. Although we caught fish, no trophies were landed but we did manage to get up close and personal with this small cow using an electric motor. This is the 3rd time it has been seen on the lake this year.....  Moose Video    Dinner......    I hope you enjoyed the moose video,  TDunn
Cool Video!!!  Always nice to capture them on video...   Nice Catch!!   Randy
Nice brookies!  I love getting up close to big game like that!
that's awesome...we saw a cow and twins last week when we where speck fishing too...we didn't get any specks though.  Nice job!
